data.description: Own a home with green energy and very low electric bills. ENERGY SCORE of 10! The owned solar panels were recently installed. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, this home offers so much for an affordable price. This delightful ranch style home has impressive updates throughout with new HVAC, new solar panels, newer water heater and newer kitchen appliances! Enjoy Portland's warm summers outside in the backyard oasis with the serenity of the water fountain on your wrap around deck. You'll regret it if you don't at least take a look inside! HOME WARRANTY PROVIDED! POSSIBLE $5000 LENDER CREDIT FOR BUYERS WHO QUALIFY. Inquire for details. [Home Energy Score = 10. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222486]
